n\"><div class=\"field-items\"><div class=\"field-item even\" property=\"content:encoded\"><p>A top adviser to the Iranian supreme leader discussed Lebanon and ceasefire negotiations, nuclear policy, and a potential Iranian response to Israels October 25 strike. Lebanese Hezbollah is likely firing large numbers of rockets at Israel to pressure the Israeli government during ongoing ceasefire negotiations. Russia reportedly recruited hundreds of Yemeni nationals to fight in the Russian military amid growing cooperation between Russia, Iran, and the Iran-backed Houthi movement.</p>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"sharethis-buttons\"><div class=\"sharethis-wrapper\"><span st_url=\"https://www.understandingwar.org/backgrounder/iran-update-november-24-2024\" st_title=\"Iran Update, November 24, 2024\" class=\"st_facebook&amp;amp;amp;quot_large\" displayText=\"facebook&amp;amp;amp;amp;quot\"></span>\n<span st_url=\"https://www.understandingwar.org/backgrounder/iran-update-november-24-2024\" st_title=\"Iran Update, November 24, 2024\" class=\"st_twitter&amp;amp;amp;quot_large\" displayText=\"twitter&amp;amp;amp;amp;quot\"></span>\n<span st_url=\"https://www.understandingwar.org/backgrounder/iran-update-november-24-2024\" st_title=\"Iran Update, November 24, 2024\" class=\"st_stumbleupon&amp;amp;amp;quot_large\" displayText=\"stumbleupon&amp;amp;amp;amp;quot\"></span>\n<span st_url=\"https://www.understandingwar.org/backgrounder/iran-update-november-24-2024\" st_title=\"Iran Update, November 24, 2024\" class=\"st_email&amp;amp;amp;quot_large\" displayText=\"email&amp;amp;amp;amp;quot\"></span>\n<span st_url=\"https://www.understandingwar.org/backgrounder/iran-update-november-24-2024\" st_title=\"Iran Update, November 24, 2024\" class=\"st_plusone_large\" displayText=\"plusone\"></span>\n<span st_url=\"https://www.understandingwar.org/backgrounder/iran-update-november-24-2024\" st_title=\"Iran Update, November 24, 2024\" class=\"st_fblike_large\" displayText=\"fblike\"></span